fwprop.entryDesc:

with failure code VER_FULL_RDL

fwprop.note:
Start Action for Commands (3,1) and (3,2) to create a new housekeeping/diagnostic report. The command carries
the information defining the new report. Command (3,1) creates a (3,25) report and command (3,2) creates a (3,26) report
